headline: Emerson Stock Gains From Business Strength, Headwinds Persist
summary: EMR gains from strength across most of its businesses and a balanced capital allocation strategy. However, weakness in the Safety & Productivity business remains concerning.

headline: Emerson Schedules Second Quarter 2025 Earnings Release and Conference Call
summary: Emerson (NYSE: EMR) will report its second quarter results prior to market open on Wednesday, May 7, 2025. Emerson senior management will discuss the results during an investor conference call that same day, beginning at 8:00 a.m. Eastern Time, 7:00 a.m. Central Time.
